  "title": "react-instantsearch-nextjs wrong import from algolia",
  "body": "### Problem\nThe readme file on the [react-instantsearch-nextjs readme](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/tree/master/packages/react-instantsearch-nextjs) is importing thew wrong algolia lite package. \n\n#### Expected\n`import { liteClient as algoliasearch } from \"algoliasearch/lite\";`\n\n#### Actual \n`import algoliasearch from 'algoliasearch/lite';`\n\n",
